1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper focuses on natural language generation tasks such as machine translation, image caption generation, and speech recognition. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper also focuses on image and video analysis tasks such as image caption generation and video clip description. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper describes the use of deep neural networks for structured output problems, which is a core topic in machine learning. 
4. cs.SD (Sound) - The paper mentions speech recognition as one of the tasks, which falls under the sound category. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper describes the use of attention mechanisms in deep neural networks, which is a popular topic in the field of artificial intelligence.
